  </div>
</div>

<!-- MAIN -->
<div class="wrap">

  <!-- WHAT'S ON OFFER -->
  <p class="section-title" style="margin-top:0.5rem">What we offer</p>
  <p class="section-sub">Simple, honest placements that feel native to the site — not banner ads that everyone ignores.</p>

  <div class="offerings-grid">

    <div class="offering-card">
      <div class="offering-stripe" style="background:#FFCB00"></div>
      <div class="offering-body">
        <div class="offering-icon">⭐</div>
        <div class="offering-title">Featured placement</div>
        <div class="offering-desc">Your deal sits at the top of the directory page in a highlighted gold card, above all organic listings. Labelled as "Sponsored" — but it looks good, not spammy. Seen by everyone who visits that week.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="offering-footer">
        <span class="offering-price">From £50 / week</span>
        <span class="offering-badge">Most popular</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="offering-card">
      <div class="offering-stripe" style="background:#6B4FBB"></div>
      <div class="offering-body">
        <div class="offering-icon">📍</div>
        <div class="offering-title">Priority listing</div>
        <div class="offering-desc">Your venue's existing deal listing is pinned to the top of its category (Happy Hour, Bottomless Brunch, etc.) with a subtle highlight. Great for venues already on the directory who want more visibility.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="offering-footer">
        <span class="offering-price">From £30 / week</span>
        <span class="offering-badge">Low effort</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="offering-card">
      <div class="offering-stripe" style="background:#2BBFAE"></div>
      <div class="offering-body">
        <div class="offering-icon">✍️</div>
        <div class="offering-title">Sponsored content</div>
        <div class="offering-desc">A dedicated write-up of your venue or deal — "Best rooftop bars in Manchester", "Top 5 happy hours in Ancoats" etc. — with your venue featured prominently. Clearly labelled, genuinely useful for readers.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="offering-footer">
        <span class="offering-price">From £100 / post</span>
        <span class="offering-badge">High impact</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="offering-card">
      <div class="offering-stripe" style="background:#E63946"></div>
      <div class="offering-body">
        <div class="offering-icon">🤝</div>
        <div class="offering-title">Venue partnership</div>
        <div class="offering-desc">A longer-term "Sorted MCR x [Your Venue]" collab — exclusive deal for our audience, joint social content on Instagram and TikTok, priority placement across the site. Revenue share or flat-fee, we're flexible.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="offering-footer">
        <span class="offering-price">Let's talk</span>
        <span class="offering-badge">Best value</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="offering-card">
      <div class="offering-stripe" style="background:#FF6B35"></div>
      <div class="offering-body">
        <div class="offering-icon">📧</div>
        <div class="offering-title">Newsletter feature</div>
        <div class="offering-desc">A sponsored slot in our weekly email — sent every week to subscribers who've opted in for Manchester's best deals. Direct line to a hyper-local, deal-hungry audience in their inbox.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="offering-footer">
        <span class="offering-price">From £40 / send</span>
        <span class="offering-badge">Growing fast</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="offering-card">
      <div class="offering-stripe" style="background:#2E7D32"></div>
      <div class="offering-body">
        <div class="offering-icon">🎯</div>
        <div class="offering-title">Get listed (free)</div>
        <div class="offering-desc">If you've got a genuine deal — happy hour, student discount, bottomless brunch — we'll add it to the directory for free. No catch. We only list deals that are actually good value. That's the whole point.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="offering-footer">
        <span class="offering-price">Free</span>
        <span class="offering-badge">Always available</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- WHAT WE WON'T DO -->
  <div class="honest-box">
    <h3>🙅 What we won't do</h3>
    <div class="honest-list">
      <div class="honest-item"><span class="icon">✗</span><span>Plaster your banner across every page (ruins the experience for everyone)</span></div>
      <div class="honest-item"><span class="icon">✗</span><span>Write fake reviews or pretend a bad deal is good</span></div>
      <div class="honest-item"><span class="icon">✗</span><span>Hide that something is sponsored (we're transparent with our audience)</span></div>
      <div class="honest-item"><span class="icon">✗</span><span>Lock you into long contracts — start small and see how it goes</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
  <p class="section-title">How it works</p>
  <p class="section-sub">Simple and fast. No lengthy onboarding, no agency faff.</p>
  <div class="process-steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">1</div>
      <div class="step-title">Get in touch</div>
      <div class="step-desc">Drop us an email with your venue, your deal and what you're looking to achieve.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">2</div>
      <div class="step-title">We agree a slot</div>
      <div class="step-desc">We'll recommend the right placement type and price, you approve the deal copy.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">3</div>
      <div class="step-title">Go live</div>
      <div class="step-desc">Your deal is live on the site (and potentially our social channels) within 24 hours.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">4</div>
      <div class="step-title">Track results</div>
      <div class="step-desc">We share basic stats — page views, click-throughs — so you can see what you're getting.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <div class="contact-section" id="contact">
    <h2>Ready to get started?</h2>
    <p>Drop us a line and we'll get back to you within 24 hours. Tell us your venue, your deal and roughly what you're looking for — we'll take it from there.</p>
